<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA2">
<l>aṭiyōmōṭu niṉṉōṭum piriviṉṟi yāyiram pallāṇṭu</l>
<l>vaṭivāyniṉ valamārpiṉil vāḻkiṉṟa maṅkaiyum pallāṇṭu</l>
<l>vaṭivārcōti valattuṟaiyuñ cuṭarāḻiyam pallāṇṭu</l>
<l>paṭaipōrpukku muḻaṅkumap pāñcacaṉṉiyamum pallāṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To the union between you and us, who are your slaves, many thousands of years!</l>
<l>To the woman who abides beautifully on your strong chest, many years!</l>
<l>To the glowing discus that dwells on the right side of [your] splendor, full of beauty, many years!</l>
<l>To the [conch called] Pāñcajanya that enters the battle of the armies and roars, many years!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
